author: COMSOL
description: This example demonstrates the Lithium-Ion Battery interface for simulation of the internal resistance and voltage loss when high current pulses are applied in a hybrid pulse power characterization (HPPC) test. Contribution to the losses from different parts of the battery are also analyzed when varying different design parameters.
